1
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:14,319
The weather today...

2
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:17,400
is really cloudless.

3
00:01:18,559 --> 00:01:20,000
It's especially perfect for...

4
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:24,519
Perfect for what?

5
00:01:25,959 --> 00:01:28,319
I've noticed your ability to make small talk

6
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:29,000
is pretty average.

7
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:29,839
What are you talking about?

8
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,080
Who's making small talk?

9
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:32,199
When I'm with you,

10
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:34,000
I have endless things to say.

11
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:37,120
But speaking of the weather,

12
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,639
it does seem a bit cliché, huh?

13
00:01:44,839 --> 00:01:46,160
Looking like a mess like this,

14
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:47,599
how can he be the president of Feimanchi?

15
00:01:48,639 --> 00:01:49,720
What president?

16
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:52,040
He doesn't even count as a normal person right now.

17
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:57,279
I'm not talking about that.

18
00:01:57,279 --> 00:01:59,279
Can a breakup make a man more mature?

19
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:01,239
Why is he like this? He went straight back to kindergarten.

20
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:04,239
It was his first love, after all.

21
00:02:04,239 --> 00:02:06,480
How can a first love be so easily forgotten?

22
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,440
First love?

23
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,000
Keep it down, keep it down.

24
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:17,399
So,

25
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:20,479
President Gu,

26
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,160
have you had any dreams lately

27
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,440
about the case?

28
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:25,839
I can't even sleep.

29
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,360
How could I have any dreams?

30
00:02:28,279 --> 00:02:30,080
This Lin Jiaqi, really...

31
00:02:30,559 --> 00:02:31,320
What's wrong with Jiaqi?

32
00:02:31,679 --> 00:02:32,360
Is she eating well?

33
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:33,320
Is she sleeping well?

34
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,520
Is she taking good care of herself?

35
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,479
Has she gotten sick?

36
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,440
Call and ask her yourself.

37
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:42,039
She won't answer my calls.

38
00:02:42,759 --> 00:02:43,600
I have to say, you

39
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,600
always drop the ball at crucial moments.

40
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:47,399
You can't even handle this properly.

41
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:49,080
How can I talk to you about the case?

42
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:50,960
Then I don't need to tell you

43
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:51,960
any information about Lin Jiaqi.

44
00:02:53,679 --> 00:02:55,479
Didn't I tell you I had a dream?

45
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:57,080
I dreamed about a watch.

46
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,240
How many times have I said it?

47
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,360
A watch can never become

48
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,679
evidence for a hit-and-run case.

49
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:01,479
Then what do you want me to do?

50
00:03:01,479 --> 00:03:02,600
Have another dream?

51
00:03:02,839 --> 00:03:05,039
I can't sleep.

52
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,119
Don't be sad, don't be sad.

53
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,440
There, there, there.

54
00:03:10,119 --> 00:03:10,759
There, there, there.

55
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:11,160
Alright, alright.

56
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:11,880
How about this,

57
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,919
let's sort this out carefully.

58
00:03:14,839 --> 00:03:15,440
If...

59
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:18,279
If that Feng Ziang is the killer,

60
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:19,839
then why didn't his car

61
00:03:20,279 --> 00:03:22,479
react to the blood test?

62
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:23,479
Right.

63
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:24,880
It's highly possible

64
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:26,440
that he scrapped the original car,

65
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,199
bought an identical one,

66
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,600
and then changed the license plate.

67
00:03:31,759 --> 00:03:32,839
Then it's easy.

68
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:33,960
Impound his car,

69
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,119
then check the engine's serial number.

70
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,279
Wouldn't that solve it?

71
00:03:37,679 --> 00:03:38,639
You suddenly became so smart.

72
00:03:38,639 --> 00:03:39,279
High five!

73
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,919
Do you think you two are Sherlock Holmes?

74
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:43,440
Wouldn't I understand this much?

75
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,759
But do you think that search warrant

76
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:46,720
just falls from the sky?

77
00:03:47,679 --> 00:03:48,320
Oh, right.

78
00:03:49,119 --> 00:03:50,520
There must be suspicions and evidence

79
00:03:50,679 --> 00:03:52,000
to apply for a search.

80
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:52,759
You know?

81
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:55,919
Then how on earth can we catch him?

82
00:03:58,039 --> 00:03:59,240
I think,

83
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:01,320
this whole thing,

84
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:03,960
ultimately comes down to Tan Feng.

85
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:06,559
I think,

86
00:04:07,119 --> 00:04:09,720
the key to this whole thing is still me.

87
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,960
As long as I go back tonight,

88
00:04:12,119 --> 00:04:13,520
rest well, and get a good sleep,

89
00:04:13,839 --> 00:04:15,360
I will definitely have a very useful dream.

90
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:16,799
Don't worry, Lin Yaoyao.

91
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,559
As long as I dream of useful clues,

92
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:19,920
I'll report to you immediately.

93
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:24,079
You can do it, President Gu!

94
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:29,359
Do you know it really hurts when you hit people?

95
00:04:34,239 --> 00:04:35,799
You hit way too hard.

96
00:04:53,119 --> 00:04:55,239
Looks like I'm really beyond cure.

97
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:58,920
I've even reached the stage of having hallucinations.

98
00:05:00,359 --> 00:05:02,200
I really need to get some good rest.

99
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:08,119
But in my hallucinations,

100
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,079
I'm still pretty happy.

101
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:17,399
Lin Jiaqi.

102
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:18,440
Is it...

103
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,359
Is it really you?

104
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,040
What's wrong?

105
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:37,200
During this time,

106
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,799
have you been staying at Lin Yaoyao's place?

107
00:05:42,359 --> 00:05:43,000
Yes.

108
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:44,760
I've been imposing on her.

109
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,839
Thanks to her taking care of me for so long.

110
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:49,720
Have you still not found a job?

111
00:05:50,679 --> 00:05:51,279
Yeah.

112
00:05:51,559 --> 00:05:52,640
It's hard to find a job right now.

113
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:53,839
I plan to

114
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,200
sell my current house,

115
00:05:55,399 --> 00:05:56,640
and move up north.

116
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,799
My grandmother happens to live there too.

117
00:05:59,279 --> 00:06:01,720
Do you really have to take things this far?

118
00:06:03,959 --> 00:06:05,000
Because there are too many

119
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,559
memories of Du Zheng and me here.

120
00:06:09,279 --> 00:06:10,119
I want to forget them

121
00:06:10,399 --> 00:06:11,679
and start over.

122
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:15,559
Choosing not to see you before

123
00:06:15,559 --> 00:06:16,640
was also for this reason.

124
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:20,119
So I hope you can accept reality soon,

125
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:22,480
and

126
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,440
face our current relationship.

127
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:26,839
Therefore,

128
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,320
I hope both of us can

129
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,839
keep going on our own paths

130
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,640
and do our best.

131
00:06:35,399 --> 00:06:37,160
I sincerely hope you'll be well.

132
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,119
Actually,

133
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,600
I've also thought about it a lot lately.

134
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:52,679
No matter what others tell you,

135
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,440
I, Gu Tiancheng,

136
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:55,959
would never like you just because

137
00:06:55,959 --> 00:06:57,600
I received Du Zheng's heart.

138
00:06:59,079 --> 00:06:59,799
I like you

139
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,040
simply because you are Lin Jiaqi.

140
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:09,640
I want to thank you for

141
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,720
staying by my side all this time.

142
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,920
In the future, I will still use my own way

143
00:07:15,799 --> 00:07:17,320
to express my feelings for you.

144
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:19,519
President.

145
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:20,320
Don't worry.

146
00:07:20,799 --> 00:07:21,559
I

147
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:23,320
won't shamelessly

148
00:07:23,679 --> 00:07:24,920
force you to accept me.

149
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:27,880
We are still good friends.

150
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,160
We both need to do our best.

151
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,399
You should go.

152
00:07:33,119 --> 00:07:33,959
I won't see you out.

153
00:07:40,079 --> 00:07:41,079
I'll be leaving then.

154
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,079
Uncle Du.

155
00:08:10,799 --> 00:08:12,119
You came out of your way to see me today.

156
00:08:12,679 --> 00:08:13,519
Is there something you need?

157
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:18,880
Nothing much.

158
00:08:23,239 --> 00:08:26,000
I just had to submit a production report.

159
00:08:26,239 --> 00:08:28,320
So I made a trip here.

160
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:36,799
After you heard the news that day,

161
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:39,880
you must have been shocked.

162
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:42,760
No.

163
00:08:45,719 --> 00:08:46,400
Really?

164
00:08:48,599 --> 00:08:49,719
Yeah.

165
00:08:53,719 --> 00:08:54,840
Actually, that day,

166
00:08:56,239 --> 00:08:57,359
I felt it was

167
00:08:57,760 --> 00:08:58,719
quite miraculous.

168
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,479
I wasn't scared.

169
00:09:03,479 --> 00:09:04,679
Actually, all this time,

170
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,159
I've felt

171
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:08,880
really sorry towards you.

172
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:17,400
This isn't something you should apologize for.

173
00:09:20,119 --> 00:09:21,159
To be honest,

174
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:25,919
I should be thanking you.

175
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,599
Because Du Zheng...

176
00:09:31,359 --> 00:09:32,679
Du Zheng is still...

177
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:35,760
still able to live on through your body.

178
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,479
For him,

179
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:42,320
it means he didn't die in vain.

180
00:09:44,159 --> 00:09:46,159
So I want to thank you.

181
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:49,640
Thank you for living so healthily.

182
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:53,000
I also hope that

183
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:55,679
in the future,

184
00:09:57,719 --> 00:10:00,039
you'll take good care of this heart.

185
00:10:06,359 --> 00:10:08,799
Jiaqi is a bit emotional right now,

186
00:10:09,159 --> 00:10:10,599
I hope you can understand.

187
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:12,960
Uncle Du.

188
00:10:13,479 --> 00:10:14,200
What?

189
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:17,320
Did you think I'd do what Feng Ziang said,

190
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:18,719
and break you two up?

191
00:10:20,359 --> 00:10:21,239
Of course not.

192
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,559
If nothing had happened,

193
00:10:23,119 --> 00:10:24,599
she would be my daughter-in-law.

194
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:26,400
From the bottom of my heart,

195
00:10:26,679 --> 00:10:28,320
I hope she can be happy.

196
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,000
So,

197
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,960
even though Du Zheng is gone,

198
00:10:32,719 --> 00:10:33,520
his share,

199
00:10:34,159 --> 00:10:35,919
I hope you can make up for it, okay?

200
00:10:38,599 --> 00:10:39,679
Don't worry, Uncle Du.

201
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,359
I definitely will.

202
00:10:43,719 --> 00:10:45,479
Actually, Jiaqi has done a lot for me too.

203
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:48,280
She's gone way beyond a secretary's duties.

204
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:49,520
By the way,

205
00:10:50,119 --> 00:10:50,840
did you know?

206
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:52,799
She actually told me once

207
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:54,719
that she wanted to protect me.

208
00:10:57,679 --> 00:10:58,599
A girl

209
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:00,440
saying what a guy should say.

210
00:11:01,479 --> 00:11:02,679
Don't you think she's very special?

211
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:13,760
Lin Jiaqi?

212
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:14,359
Yes.

213
00:11:14,359 --> 00:11:15,080
Your delivery.

214
00:11:15,599 --> 00:11:15,919
Thank you.

215
00:11:15,919 --> 00:11:16,359
No problem.

216
00:11:16,479 --> 00:11:16,960
Here you go.

217
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,280
Lin Jiaqi.

218
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,400
If you dare throw the flowers away,

219
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:40,840
you will face divine punishment.

220
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:54,400
Come back here!

221
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:55,520
Take the flowers away!

222
00:12:10,799 --> 00:12:12,359
I said this is my punishment.

223
00:12:12,799 --> 00:12:14,119
I will keep sending you flowers

224
00:12:14,799 --> 00:12:15,880
until I die.

225
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,119
It's Tan Feng.

226
00:12:36,159 --> 00:12:37,559
What exactly is going on with you?

227
00:12:38,919 --> 00:12:41,039
The hospital hasn't received a single cent from you yet.

228
00:12:42,479 --> 00:12:43,280
I forgot.

229
00:12:44,719 --> 00:12:45,599
But...

230
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,280
Why should I pay for you?

231
00:12:47,599 --> 00:12:48,359
What did you say?

232
00:12:48,919 --> 00:12:50,400
Bring the memory card to trade with me.

233
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,200
Don't even think about it.

234
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,400
If I give the thing to you,

235
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:56,559
would you still pay attention to a nobody like me?

236
00:12:57,559 --> 00:12:58,280
Right now,

237
00:12:58,559 --> 00:13:00,039
I still have leverage over you.

238
00:13:00,599 --> 00:13:02,159
You can still discuss things with me.

239
00:13:02,599 --> 00:13:03,840
Give me the memory card,

240
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,520
and I'll go to Japan immediately.

241
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,320
What are you going to Japan for?

242
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:09,359
I found a kidney.

243
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:10,599
Really?

244
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:15,119
Tell me, a fresh kidney in a freezer,

245
00:13:15,719 --> 00:13:16,799
how long can it be kept?

246
00:13:18,039 --> 00:13:19,239
You're not lying to me, are you?

247
00:13:21,119 --> 00:13:22,119
Believe it or not, it's up to you.

248
00:13:22,479 --> 00:13:23,760
Anyway, I'm not the one who needs a kidney transplant.

249
00:13:28,599 --> 00:13:30,559
How much has the revenue of the new products grown recently?

250
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,679
Compared to the initial production phase,

251
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,320
it has increased by about three times.

252
00:13:34,599 --> 00:13:36,119
Those that originally refused our entry,

253
00:13:36,119 --> 00:13:37,200
the two department stores,

254
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,960
have also invited us back.

255
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:41,719
That's great.

256
00:13:42,599 --> 00:13:44,159
Now that our company is improving,

257
00:13:44,640 --> 00:13:46,280
we no longer have to humble ourselves

258
00:13:46,559 --> 00:13:47,880
to beg others to sign contracts with us.

259
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:48,719
Of course.

260
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,840
And the issue with our soon-to-expire bonds

261
00:13:51,039 --> 00:13:52,359
can also be easily resolved.

262
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:53,799
Okay.

263
00:13:54,799 --> 00:13:55,320
By the way,

264
00:13:56,119 --> 00:13:57,640
remember to readjust

265
00:13:57,640 --> 00:13:58,559
the store's operating expenses.

266
00:13:58,760 --> 00:13:59,359
Okay, okay.

267
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:03,239
Let's end today's meeting here.

268
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:04,559
Okay.

269
00:14:20,679 --> 00:14:21,559
Today,

270
00:14:22,119 --> 00:14:23,000
I wish you good luck.

271
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:31,400
Hello, I'm Lin Jiaqi.

272
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:32,599
This is my resume.

273
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:35,239
Please have a seat.

274
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,039
Miss Lin,

275
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:40,359
did you work at Feimanchi before?

276
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:41,559
Yes.

277
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,880
I was the president's secretary.

278
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,760
Being able to work at Feimanchi

279
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:45,919
is certainly not simple.

280
00:14:46,599 --> 00:14:47,719
We all agree that you

281
00:14:47,719 --> 00:14:49,520
are very suitable for this position in our company.

282
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:52,919
Does that mean I'm hired?

283
00:14:53,479 --> 00:14:54,719
We warmly welcome Miss Lin

284
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,200
to come work at our company.

285
00:15:00,679 --> 00:15:01,359
Senior,

286
00:15:02,119 --> 00:15:03,239
Tan Feng's car has appeared.

287
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:05,080
Are you sure?

288
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:06,520
I'm sure. Everything matches up.

289
00:15:06,520 --> 00:15:07,200
Let's go, let's go.

290
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:17,760
Feng Ziang!

291
00:15:20,119 --> 00:15:21,200
Come out here!

292
00:15:21,679 --> 00:15:22,919
Didn't you ask me to come?

293
00:15:23,039 --> 00:15:23,599
Come on!

294
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:26,559
You don't want the thing anymore, right?

295
00:15:27,039 --> 00:15:28,159
Are you messing with me?

296
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:45,200
Who are you guys?

297
00:15:45,400 --> 00:15:46,320
I don't know you.

298
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:48,440
We're here on someone's behalf to teach a lesson

299
00:15:48,599 --> 00:15:49,799
to a dog that tries to bite its master.

300
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,280
You... Are you...

301
00:15:52,799 --> 00:15:54,080
Did Feng Ziang send you?

302
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:57,000
We're just getting paid to fix a problem.

303
00:15:57,359 --> 00:15:58,159
Where's the memory card?

304
00:15:58,640 --> 00:15:59,200
Hand it over.

305
00:15:59,599 --> 00:16:00,280
What card?

306
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:01,440
I don't know.

307
00:16:02,239 --> 00:16:02,719
You don't know?

308
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:04,359
I don't know!

309
00:16:05,880 --> 00:16:06,080
Beat him.

310
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:09,640
Stop hitting me!

311
00:16:10,400 --> 00:16:10,880
Stop hitting me!

312
00:16:10,880 --> 00:16:11,520
Stop hitting me!

313
00:16:11,719 --> 00:16:12,320
Where's the card?

314
00:16:13,599 --> 00:16:14,119
What card?

315
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:14,840
What do you mean, what card?

316
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,359
I really don't have it!

317
00:16:15,760 --> 00:16:16,119
Where's the card?

318
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:18,679
Run! It's the police!

319
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:19,440
Run!

320
00:16:24,280 --> 00:16:24,640
Stop right there!

321
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:25,440
Don't run!

322
00:16:25,719 --> 00:16:26,239
Stop!

323
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:31,479
Brother Feng.

324
00:16:31,880 --> 00:16:32,679
Brother Feng, Brother Feng.

325
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:35,400
What happened?

326
00:16:36,239 --> 00:16:37,159
When Gu Rongchen was around,

327
00:16:37,159 --> 00:16:38,239
I kept you guys on the payroll.

328
00:16:38,919 --> 00:16:40,239
Now that he's dead, you've gone stupid?

329
00:16:40,799 --> 00:16:42,200
We're really sorry, Brother Feng.

330
00:16:42,679 --> 00:16:43,200
Next time...

331
00:16:43,479 --> 00:16:44,919
Next time, we'll definitely get it done right.

332
00:16:45,119 --> 00:16:45,880
Next time?

333
00:16:46,239 --> 00:16:47,440
Do you guys even have brains?

334
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:48,599
You either

335
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,000
get me the memory card,

336
00:16:50,440 --> 00:16:51,479
or you catch the guy.

337
00:16:51,919 --> 00:16:52,640
But look at you now.

338
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,400
You didn't get the item, and the guy got away.

339
00:16:55,039 --> 00:16:56,039
We lost both the man and the prize.

340
00:16:56,239 --> 00:16:57,239
What are you even good for?

341
00:16:57,479 --> 00:16:58,320
No, Brother Feng.

342
00:16:58,559 --> 00:16:59,239
Here's what happened.

343
00:16:59,599 --> 00:17:01,000
When we caught Tan Feng,

344
00:17:01,119 --> 00:17:01,760
we didn't know...

345
00:17:01,760 --> 00:17:02,479
Suddenly, out of nowhere,

346
00:17:02,479 --> 00:17:03,679
two cops popped up.

347
00:17:03,880 --> 00:17:05,280
We had no choice but to run.

348
00:17:05,959 --> 00:17:07,359
So Tan Feng managed to escape.

349
00:17:08,359 --> 00:17:09,040
How about this?

350
00:17:09,199 --> 00:17:10,319
I'll go look for him in a bit.

351
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:12,280
When I find him, I'll beat him up good

352
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:13,599
to help you vent your anger.

353
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:16,119
Vent my anger?

354
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:18,000
I'll only vent my anger if you guys die!

355
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:19,400
Do you have a brain?

356
00:17:20,079 --> 00:17:21,520
You've already crossed paths with the cops.

357
00:17:21,680 --> 00:17:23,000
You're lucky they aren't looking for you.

358
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:24,400
Good lord,

359
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:26,959
and now you want to stick your neck out to find him?

360
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:30,839
Then what do you suggest we... we...

361
00:17:32,319 --> 00:17:33,280
Things are pretty tense lately.

362
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:34,439
Go lay low somewhere.

363
00:17:34,439 --> 00:17:35,640
Okay, will do.

364
00:17:35,959 --> 00:17:36,760
I'll find you if I need anything.

365
00:17:36,760 --> 00:17:37,400
Okay.

366
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:38,880
Take care, Brother Feng.

367
00:17:45,560 --> 00:17:46,079
This is bad!

368
00:17:46,839 --> 00:17:47,520
This is bad!

369
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:48,640
This is bad!

370
00:17:49,119 --> 00:17:50,719
What's with all the fuss so early in the morning?

371
00:17:50,719 --> 00:17:51,800
We're being sued!

372
00:17:53,560 --> 00:17:54,319
Sued?

373
00:17:55,319 --> 00:17:56,119
Sued for what?

374
00:17:56,520 --> 00:17:59,199
They said it's a patent lawsuit over the new product's base ingredients.

375
00:17:59,319 --> 00:17:59,760
Moreover,

376
00:17:59,760 --> 00:18:01,160
they've also applied for a sales suspension.

377
00:18:01,439 --> 00:18:02,040
Which means,

378
00:18:02,239 --> 00:18:03,359
we can't sell our products anymore.

379
00:18:05,800 --> 00:18:06,239
Let's go.

380
00:18:06,599 --> 00:18:07,839
Rosen Company has filed a patent lawsuit

381
00:18:07,839 --> 00:18:09,959
over the launch of our new product.

382
00:18:10,280 --> 00:18:11,880
But haven't we already obtained the patent?

383
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:13,680
They insist that they applied for it first.

384
00:18:15,079 --> 00:18:16,520
No wonder they've been so quiet lately.

385
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:18,920
It must be that Jerk Feng Ziang's doing.

386
00:18:19,199 --> 00:18:20,439
In that case, until the lawsuit is over,

387
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,239
we won't be able to sell a single product.

388
00:18:22,719 --> 00:18:23,079
Exactly.

389
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:31,719
A person who studied law

390
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:34,800
finally made good use of his major.

391
00:18:35,439 --> 00:18:36,920
What I've done over the past six years

392
00:18:37,479 --> 00:18:38,319
has given me

393
00:18:38,719 --> 00:18:40,040
a more comprehensive analysis of the law.

394
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:42,439
Why can't I hear anything

395
00:18:42,439 --> 00:18:43,479
worth showing off about this?

396
00:18:44,520 --> 00:18:46,359
I'm telling you as a legal expert,

397
00:18:47,599 --> 00:18:48,760
they will fight this lawsuit

398
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:49,880
to the bitter end.

399
00:18:50,119 --> 00:18:50,800
What's the situation?

400
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:51,800
Of course,

401
00:18:52,439 --> 00:18:52,959
President Gu,

402
00:18:53,239 --> 00:18:54,760
you must not be anxious.

403
00:18:55,319 --> 00:18:56,359
Because no matter what,

404
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:57,920
you will win this lawsuit.

405
00:18:59,319 --> 00:19:00,479
That should be

406
00:19:01,239 --> 00:19:02,000
three years from now.

407
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:04,119
By that time,

408
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:07,119
Feimanchi might have already gone bankrupt.

409
00:19:08,040 --> 00:19:10,040
Export volume and domestic distribution contracts,

410
00:19:10,599 --> 00:19:12,239
that's not just a matter of a few million.

411
00:19:14,239 --> 00:19:16,239
Then use the previous advance payments

412
00:19:16,560 --> 00:19:17,560
to make up for it.

413
00:19:27,839 --> 00:19:28,400
Come,

414
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:29,920
take a look.

415
00:19:30,359 --> 00:19:31,920
With this location and this price,

416
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:33,400
you definitely won't find

417
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,359
anything better than this.

418
00:19:34,839 --> 00:19:35,880
It's well-ventilated from north to south,

419
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:38,800
and the lighting and ventilation are both excellent.

420
00:19:39,079 --> 00:19:39,719
Of course,

421
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:42,119
mainly, it's very close to your company, young lady.

422
00:19:42,479 --> 00:19:44,359
If the landlord wasn't in a hurry to go abroad

423
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:46,599
and afraid of having no time to handle this later,

424
00:19:46,959 --> 00:19:47,920
this house

425
00:19:48,119 --> 00:19:49,520
could be at any price.

426
00:19:50,560 --> 00:19:51,560
I think it's pretty good too.

427
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:53,040
When can we sign the contract?

428
00:19:53,359 --> 00:19:54,319
Anytime.

429
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:56,359
Excuse me.

430
00:19:58,680 --> 00:19:59,359
Uncle Du.

431
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:00,599
Uncle.

432
00:20:01,359 --> 00:20:03,119
Did you need me for something?

433
00:20:03,280 --> 00:20:04,000
Nothing much.

434
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:05,880
It's just been a long time since we last met.

435
00:20:06,239 --> 00:20:07,880
I wanted to have a meal and chat with you.

436
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:13,400
After that incident last time,

437
00:20:13,760 --> 00:20:15,119
we haven't seen each other.

438
00:20:18,839 --> 00:20:19,439
By the way,

439
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:22,119
I heard you're leaving here, is that right?

440
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:24,520
Yes.

441
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:27,479
Have you found a job and everything?

442
00:20:27,959 --> 00:20:29,319
I've found both a job and a place to live.

443
00:20:30,040 --> 00:20:30,760
That's good.

444
00:20:31,439 --> 00:20:32,199
That's really good.

445
00:20:34,119 --> 00:20:35,560
It's quite strange when you think about it.

446
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:37,680
Ever since I resigned,

447
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:39,239
everything has been going very smoothly.

448
00:20:40,319 --> 00:20:41,239
My mood

449
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:42,959
has also lightened up a lot.

450
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:44,599
Actually, coming back to it,

451
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,479
I should thank President Gu.

452
00:20:49,319 --> 00:20:50,599
Seeing Du Zheng's heart

453
00:20:51,439 --> 00:20:53,479
continue to beat in his body,

454
00:20:54,119 --> 00:20:55,319
I should thank him.

455
00:21:00,680 --> 00:21:01,599
By the way, Jiaqi,

456
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:03,839
I heard President Gu say

457
00:21:04,280 --> 00:21:05,680
that you want to protect him, is that right?

458
00:21:07,199 --> 00:21:08,119
That's because

459
00:21:11,760 --> 00:21:14,520
Du Zheng was the one who silently protected you,

460
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:17,800
while President Gu is the one you want to protect.

461
00:21:19,079 --> 00:21:20,119
In other words,

462
00:21:20,719 --> 00:21:21,959
you are using different ways

463
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:23,920
to love two men at the same time, right?

464
00:21:25,319 --> 00:21:26,319
I really don't want

465
00:21:26,959 --> 00:21:28,239
such a good girl like you

466
00:21:28,239 --> 00:21:29,479
to be unhappy for the rest of your life.

467
00:21:33,239 --> 00:21:34,400
Uncle came today

468
00:21:36,439 --> 00:21:37,800
to ask a favor of you.

469
00:21:39,119 --> 00:21:41,079
I just hope you can always remember

470
00:21:42,359 --> 00:21:43,560
that in your life,

471
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:46,880
there once appeared

472
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:49,319
such a lovely man.

473
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:51,040
That's enough.

474
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:52,599
Okay?
